@startuml
' @id(SEQ-RENDER-CYCLE-DIFF)
' @ref(USE-CYCLE-DIFF-VIEW)
'
' Current-side flow as implemented: MddViewer::diff_ui ->
' Project::cycle_diffs -> cycle::cycle_diffs -> diff_documents,
' rendered as colored element-key lists in the Diff tab.
'
' @desc(SEQ-RENDER-CYCLE-DIFF, "As-built diff view: diff_ui caches Project::cycle_diffs(n); element keys are partitioned by cycle::diff_documents and painted neutral/green/red.")
title Render a cycle's superposed before/after diff (current)

actor "Developer" as Dev
participant "MddViewer::diff_ui\n(eframe::App)" as Viewer
participant "Project::cycle_diffs\n(mdd-core)" as Core
participant "CycleRegistry::scan\ncycle::cycle_diffs" as Reg
database ".mdd/cycles/<N>/\nbefore/ , after/" as Store
participant "diff_documents\n(element_keys)" as Diff
participant "egui ScrollArea" as Painter

Dev -> Viewer : Diff tab, select cycle N
Viewer -> Core : cycle_diffs(N)
Core -> Reg : scan .mdd/cycles/ + resolve N
Reg -> Store : read before/ + after/ *.puml
Store --> Reg : docs
Reg -> Diff : diff_documents(name, before, after)
note right of Diff
  element_keys = every @id, plus declared
  PlantUML elements by alias/quoted label.
  unchanged = before INTERSECT after
  added     = after MINUS before
  removed   = before MINUS after
  (disjoint by construction)
end note
Diff --> Reg : CycleDiff { unchanged, added, removed }
Reg --> Core : Vec<CycleDiff>
Core --> Viewer : cached (number, diffs)

alt cycle still open (no after/)
  Viewer -> Painter : "diff available after the cycle closes"
else closed
  loop each CycleDiff
    Viewer -> Painter : shared keys (neutral)
    Viewer -> Painter : "+ added" (green)
    Viewer -> Painter : "- removed" (red, strikethrough)
  end
end
Painter --> Dev : superposed element diff
@enduml
